WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.260
I finished my artwork of Misato-chan.

00:02.260 --> 00:04.600
It was very popular in class.

00:04.600 --> 00:07.580
It’s very pretty and artful.

00:08.240 --> 00:13.600
I bet it will stand out and draw attention at the culture fair.

00:14.180 --> 00:19.040
I used pastels and watercolors.

00:19.480 --> 00:25.040
Misato-chan said that I did a good job, but I wonder if I really ought to have done a painting of her.

00:26.900 --> 00:30.240
I feel that I haven’t expressed myself as much as I wanted in my painting.

00:30.720 --> 00:33.300
What kind of painting should I do?

00:33.920 --> 00:37.560
Misato-chan’s paintings seem like Misato-chan’s.

00:38.120 --> 00:43.480
They are gentle and pretty, and seem to have an inner strength...
